      • pollLatestWith

        public default T pollLatestWith​(String description,
                                Runnable action)
        Defines an action to be performed on the starting of the polling. It is supposed the polled messages is the result of the action. Also, it changes the property ConsumerConfig.AUTO_OFFSET_RESET_CONFIG of current consumer to 'latest'. Without pollLatestWith(String, Runnable) the value 'earliest' is used.
        Parameters:
        description - description of performed action
        action - is the action to be performed
        Returns:
        self-reference
